  ; ==================== TITLE AND DOCUMENTATION ====================
  (text "SAFETY INTERLOCK SYSTEM\n\nProtection Layers:\n1. OCP: TLV3201 comparator, 50A threshold\n2. OVP: TLV3201 comparator, 390V threshold\n3. Thermal: TLV3201 w/ hysteresis, 85C trip\n4. Watchdog: TPS3823-33, 1.6s timeout\n\nFault Logic:\n- 74HC4075: Triple 3-input OR (fault combine)\n- 74HC00: Quad NAND (SR latch)\n- 74HC08: Quad AND (reset logic)\n- 74HC04: Hex inverter\n\nResponse Times:\n- OCP: 33ns detection + 50ns logic = 83ns\n- OVP: 9ns detection + 50ns logic = 59ns\n- Thermal: <1ms\n- WDT: 1.6s timeout\n\nReference: SAFETY_INTERLOCK_DESIGN.md"
    (exclude_from_sim no)
    (at 25.4 25.4 0)
    (effects (font (size 1.8 1.8)) (justify left))
    (uuid "41000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001")
  )

